comment: This scene was one of the best I´ve seen so far. The song makes it even more intense, and now I listen to Unkle daily. Looks like Unkle´s music and Person of interest were destined to be together.
I remember watching this first season and before this scene i was thinking hmm i'm not sure i will stick with this and then this happened and i was addicted. Really moving scene in a weird way.
I loved this scene. This was not what Carter signed on for. Push comes to shove, she always tried to do the right thing.
Thank you - one of the best scenes x
